  "description": "A Feynman diagram generator and amplitude calculator for particle physics with a Python API, browser UI, and packaged FastAPI service. Supports tree- and one-loop amplitudes, LO/NLO cross-sections (analytic K-factors, tabulated LHC ratios, Catani-Seymour subtraction, OpenLoops virtuals, EW Sudakov LL+NLL), differential observables, and PDF-convolved hadronic predictions.",
